130
00:26:31,759 --> 00:26:32,799
[SPEAKER_03] Voda ili bolest?

131
00:26:33,839 --> 00:26:34,000
[SPEAKER_03] Šta?

132
00:26:34,319 --> 00:26:37,440
[SPEAKER_03] Ne, definirati vas kao bolest, recimo rodna disforija ili.

133
00:26:37,599 --> 00:26:38,559
[SPEAKER_01] A, još kratko.

134
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:43,680
[SPEAKER_03] Da, rodna disforija ili rodna bolest.

135
00:26:43,839 --> 00:26:47,359
[SPEAKER_02] Da, do jučer nešto može biti bolest, sutra već može biti stanje.

136
00:26:49,519 --> 00:26:53,599
