165
00:28:29,599 --> 00:28:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] A da, to znači.

166
00:28:31,119 --> 00:28:31,839
[SPEAKER_01] Odlično, da.

167
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:33,200
[SPEAKER_01] Non-trans.

168
00:28:33,759 --> 00:28:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da, novi standard.

